{"tid":198943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梅姐當年有冇食過劉德華同謝霆鋒?","createTime":"2017-04-12T23:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T01:53:29.000Z","uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75baac2e25c624da7d10f10ebdcbb814996cacac","tid":198943,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:04:24.000Z","msg":"張國榮出席台北第28屆台灣電影金馬獎，憑《阿飛正傳》入圍最佳男主角，他和梅艷芳的合影時，<ins>阿梅輕撫他臉頰</ins>。 <br />\n<br />\n有指阿梅暗戀劉德華近10年，可惜二人有緣無份，但華仔仍視她為好朋友。兩人常在舞台上打情罵俏，一次演唱會結束時男粉絲向阿梅送花，並笑說要求婚，阿梅回應：可惜你不是劉德華，不然我就嫁給你吧！ <br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒與阿梅曾傳出緋聞,阿梅患病期間，謝霆鋒常陪伴她"},{"pid":"5df89bebd54e82857c5f11c07f141bb1dd771ac8","tid":198943,"uid":51585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:08:16.000Z","msg":"梅姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb053dd5d7b2f171bc07fa3285e295285f87960","tid":198943,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個嘴好厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebdea94c3661b4764bf39f2bd9036b469016542","tid":198943,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:15:54.000Z","msg":"梅姐都死左咁耐 死者為大 希望樓主積下口德"},{"pid":"043365fb6ae70f8820da392dddf02ca2cec7d5c2","tid":198943,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梅姐都死左咁耐 死者為大 希望樓主積下口德</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69194a1e4760bf0a585dedabcab928a8f869ad0d","tid":198943,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi